        <div class="comparison-col them">
          <h4>Cloud Assistants</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Your data lives on their servers</li>
            <li>Capped messages per month</li>
            <li>They can read everything your family says</li>
            <li>Subscription only — you own nothing</li>
            <li>Dependent on their uptime & policies</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="comparison-col us">
          <h4>FamCloud Labs</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Your data lives on your hardware</li>
            <li>Unlimited use, no caps ever</li>
            <li>Nothing leaves your home</li>
            <li>Own your device, pay for support</li>
            <li>Self-healing — it recovers itself</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
